title: My Eurodance Collection (U96, 2 Unlimited, Dune etc.)
description:
This is my Eurodance collection ... ok, not everything is strictly Eurodance :)

All the MP3s are ripped from the CDs that I bought in the 90s. They are all 320 kbps.

There are some rare and hard to find items.

Enjoy!
